{"tid":440096,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]數碼暴龍Linkz(39) 趁有得抖好抖喇","createTime":"2017-10-18T12:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T12:37:18.000Z","uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c423c76c5b2e58bcc9df50a121880b236397a8c1","tid":440096,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">15/10/2017 updated</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B439Qf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB439Qf.jpg&h=f786faa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">註:呢度充滿懞撚 講野毫不留情 如閣下為玻璃心請注意</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際服新手問題整合喺#3</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入門篇</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：首抽刷邊隻好？邊隻最勁？ <br />\nA：並無最勁，有太多分歧進化，揀隻最岩你自己開局<br />\n有人會刷盾/隊長技/繼承技 自己諗 唔好再問邊隻好唔好 亦都唔好再問進邊隻好</span><br />\n<br />\nQ：技能之後有無得變? <br />\nA： 固定技會隨住進化變，繼承技可以靠道場轉，要用a食b (b需要滿等) 咁a招繼承會變左b果招 b食完會消失。隊長技無得改。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：運有咩用? <br />\nA：任務額外獎勵。強化食同種族有機會升。越高運，出獎勵的機會率越高，100運必出。運獎勵只計隊長。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：強化 同 耐性變化係咩黎？ <br />\nA：強化 A食B A加EXP B消失 強化暫時作用：食同種族有機會升運 <br />\n耐性變化　去道場 食相同寵同進化素材 隨機加一個耐性(紅色) 被食寵會消失 <br />\n*食越高級升運機會越高 食究極體必升 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*係運UP event期間食完全體必升</span><br />\n<br />\n註1: 如果你洗左新既火抗性 <br />\n你進化之後果隻寵原本無火抗呢 新既火抗就會留低 <br />\n但你進化之後果隻寵原本已經有火抗呢 新既火抗就會自己洗左做其他抗性 <br />\n註2: 可以進行多次耐性變化, 但耐性變化只有一個 <br />\n<br />\nQ：隻GAME有無得聯機架? <br />\nA：想pvp就禁第二個島個競技場。想協力就開任之後揀右下角紅色粒制。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：如何賣寵 <br />\nA：去屋仔一覽 お別れ <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*現時賣究極體會返還碎片,但極度不建議咁做</span><br />\n<br />\nQ：最多得30體?有無得升上限架? <br />\nA：升級圓形屋頂既建築物 (施設右下レストラン 餐廳) <br />\n當完成時你一禁佢就會回哂所有體 <br />\n主升呢間同肉田 PS:用哂體力先好禁完成升級 <br />\n<br />\nQ：食肉個到要自己禁制標百勁幾下咁勁煩 <br />\nA：長禁即可加多d <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">刷EXP：8-4或者等EXP關 <br />\n刷錢：快就19-4 慢就3-3- 或者等錢關 <br />\n刷友情: 8-4 / 分身抽ticket,正身R場有10友情一場</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Lihkg</span>好友表<br />\n<br />\n新整登記表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1twht4CI8f-rWBK1WsaOXOQfbz2pqdioXZgU4YKMbniE/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1twht4CI8f-rWBK1WsaOXOQfbz2pqdioXZgU4YKMbniE%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=dcde2d3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1twht4CI8f-rWBK1WsaOXOQfbz2pqdioXZgU4YKMbniE/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n填Form<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSft1gXJaMujHDP_C_ds-PTtD_PLdsB8-oXDa1fpbB8PwffsnQ/viewform?usp=sf_link#responses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSft1gXJaMujHDP_C_ds-PTtD_PLdsB8-oXDa1fpbB8PwffsnQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link%23responses&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=b802278c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSft1gXJaMujHDP_C_ds-PTtD_PLdsB8-oXDa1fpbB8PwffsnQ/viewform?usp=sf_link#responses</a><br />\n<br />\n主要遊戲資訊網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://digimonlinkz.gamewith.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigimonlinkz.gamewith.jp%2F&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=cbfa557e\" target=\"_blank\">https://digimonlinkz.gamewith.jp/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www65.atwiki.jp/digimon_linkz/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fdigimon_linkz%2F&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=8198aacc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www65.atwiki.jp/digimon_linkz/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>1001請copy範本開post</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新template: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1PDtrXipG9wse7VHxuWAPqgRZe3Tb0AEj36rOEHZq4OU/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1PDtrXipG9wse7VHxuWAPqgRZe3Tb0AEj36rOEHZq4OU%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=59575fee\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1PDtrXipG9wse7VHxuWAPqgRZe3Tb0AEj36rOEHZq4OU/edit?usp=sharing</a></span>"},{"pid":"2af4d8a6cc640038e26ab034f479b6ca2cdbf5ff","tid":440096,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:34:23.000Z","msg":"進階篇:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：V2要用咩材料進化?<br />\nA：+4究極體VUP到V2要3粒圓形物體+35碎片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/225422_8553fae91e3e3e49ac3f42532a1b4d29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F225422_8553fae91e3e3e49ac3f42532a1b4d29.png&h=38f63780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n刷狀態抗要3粒方形物體+15碎片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/225512_57b353f8c0365e0672313caa82a880b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F225512_57b353f8c0365e0672313caa82a880b4.png&h=93655662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有關覺醒: <br />\n(好似係) <br />\n主體(左邊) 肥料(右邊) 均為究極體 <br />\n主體必須滿友情 肥料唔使 如果主體唔滿友情會覺醒唔到 <br />\n必定繼承主體盾牌  <br />\n必定繼承主體繼承技及隊長技 <br />\n<br />\n+1後要11碎先進到究極體 +2要14碎 +3同+4各要21碎 <br />\n<br />\n有關才能開花(過盾):<br />\n(好似係) <br />\n主體(左邊)成長期到究極體都無影響<br />\n肥料(右邊)升到究極體會大大提高過盾成功率,而成長期則為最低成功率<br />\n當主體過盾部位重係銀盾(1-5級)嘅時候,副體金盾係無法成功過繼,詳情請留意開花介面下面個表格<br />\n*過盾up event 一個月開放一次,到時會有1.5倍機率UP(爆)如果想變勁請留石抽盾<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e8cc2f93c19043419fbb1106ba31d86a2234f2e7","tid":440096,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"究極體碎片篇:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：究極體碎片點有？<br />\nA：<br />\n1:打降臨，降臨關卡會跌普通進化素材同究極體碎片。<br />\n下附降臨時間表,通常會係咁Loop,呢啲都係一般究極體,但某啲可以Version up去V2,有使用價值<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/230454_092157c0d6129d7b1f354d2537217210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F230454_092157c0d6129d7b1f354d2537217210.jpg&h=61f881ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2:打event，每個event都會維持一個星期,通常會出特別究極體,例如十三皇騎同七大魔王<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n另外重有隻超麻煩Linkz原創封面龍,新人一般唔建議整<br />\n下附垃圾龍進化需求<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/144841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F144841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ec38458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/145318_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F145318_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=da85a5cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">PVP 強弱獸參考表,有咩唔滿意請搵OFF巴上訴<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/003432_2a54ac4cc1cc10037fc5b3743e89a300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F003432_2a54ac4cc1cc10037fc5b3743e89a300.jpg&h=f6e40d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[例如維京上A,白奧落B之類]</span><br />\n同樣off 巴嘅資訊：各熱門寵爆擊（crit)率表<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/230634_69b7baffecdfa6c7d9afcff27781e936.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F230634_69b7baffecdfa6c7d9afcff27781e936.png&h=7631347b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d8955125d252c525f5aaf35e057d2f7509f2132","tid":440096,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">整合By WANDA巴</span><br />\n<br />\n國際ser d新手問題其實有d舊post都有人問左/game入面都有得睇<br />\n係咁易整理左(抄左部份巴打既答案/建議)希望唔好再重覆問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新手包課金揀邊隻好</strong></span><br />\n- 因為呢個新手包係得+1, 最後你都係會覺醒左佢去到+4, 但岩岩開始玩一定唔夠素材同冇究極碎升佢做+2~+4, 所以呢隻用黎做前期打event/素材用都夠做, 點揀就以稀有程度為主for日後用<br />\n1. 古狼隊長技 傑斯獸<br />\n2. 古魔隊長技 劍皇獸<br />\n3. 古龍隊長技 顱骨獸<br />\nGame入面list埋你課果隻會係乜技能, 自己睇啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首抽隊長 繼承 金盾 覺醒 嘅重要性點分?</span></strong><br />\n- +4究極 &gt; 金盾 &gt; 大隊長技 &gt; V繼技 &gt; 銀盾 &gt; 其他<br />\n[隊長技係天生冇得後天改; 繼承可以後天改; 盾都係可以用&quot;才能開花&quot;後天將B身上既盾過去A度 (但有機會過唔到)]<br />\n- +0 ~ +1其實咩究極唔算重要,呢個首抽如果抽唔到+2以上其實都未必要抽,因為每日login有劵送,又有降臨入門,拎+0/+1究極體其實唔難, 留下石應付下bamdie之後嘅垃圾event重好<br />\n- 以上只係建議, 冇話抽到咩先係最好, 更加冇話抽唔到咩就玩唔落去<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咩屬嘅金盾比較好?</span></strong><br />\n- 睇係咩寵,魔攻寵就魔攻金, etc.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>盾lv點升?</strong></span><br />\n- 用才能開花過盾or升盾lv, 通常等開花up先過盾/up盾 (成功機會比平時大1.5倍), 有盾既副寵最好係升做究極體, 否則成功機率會低d<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>進化路線點睇?</strong></span><br />\n- Game內有圖鑑<br />\n- 清楚d既可以dl呢個post入面既: <a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=28833&amp;snA=3089&amp;tnum=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D28833%26snA%3D3089%26tnum%3D114&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=53f31f0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=28833&amp;snA=3089&amp;tnum=114</a> (好耐冇update但一定夠新手用)<br />\n- 日文version: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/digimon_linkz/pages/12.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fdigimon_linkz%2Fpages%2F12.html&d=CYNFZRFoNhlE14fxwxRrKgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=405f63f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/digimon_linkz/pages/12.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新手刷200石首抽教學:協力頭10場=100石 協力11-50場,每場3石,總共120石,協力好友頭10場=100石</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊by 燉益力多巴打</span><br />\n<br />\n怪可以分2<span style=\"color: pink;\">/3</span>種用途, 1種係對戰用(PVP競技場), 另1種係用黎刷素材 ,<span style=\"color: pink;\"> 高機會event bonus角色(無人預知到)</span><br />\n第1類嘅例子:墜天地獄獸, 你可以上網睇到佢係高血高攻高防高速+最高威力&amp;多段(高爆擊)單體技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第2類嘅例子:劍皇,機邪etc. 全體多段技, 刷素材一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">第3類嘅例子: 皇騎系列, e.g. Alpha, OMG, 某d event會列明用某d怪有bonus<br />\n(最好每隻皇騎都有, 其他盡量儲啦)</span><br />\n<br />\n注: 後期會有樣叫屬性技能晶片嘅嘢裝咗會每hit都加威力<br />\n      墜天原本 暗單體 75 x 8 = 600<br />\n      配暗技晶後 (75+35) x 8 = 880<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n      所以多段技嘅都留意下<br />\n<br />\n初期通常刷弱點抗, 相剋屬性最好<br />\ne.g. 水火相剋, 戰暴(火屬火固有技)會刷水抗, 咁就可以吊打D電腦<br />\n繼技...初期應該唔洗諗住"},{"pid":"9081d78aec91146f65c6a56eb40ae3ee50964d28","tid":440096,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"呢個post 開錯咗吹水台<br />\n<br />\n轉新post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/440100/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/440100/page/1</a>"}]}